<li><strong>Instructor mobile check-in</strong> via app</li>
<li><strong>Attendance history</strong> per student</li>
<li><strong>Attendance requirements</strong> for rank eligibility</li>
<li><strong>No-show tracking</strong> and follow-up triggers</li>
</ul>

<h3>5. Instructor Availability Management</h3>

<p>Managing instructor schedules across multiple people requires dedicated functionality:</p>

